2026-05-03T23:13:04.2201158Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2201819Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2202431Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2203227Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2203986Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2204843Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2205697Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2206579Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2207433Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2208257Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2209776Z 33    -->
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2210478Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2211592Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:5-79
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2212695Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:22-76
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2213731Z 35    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_EXACT_ALARM" />
