2026-05-03T23:13:04.2220894Z 38        Used on Samsung and other OEM devices that aggressively optimize
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2221776Z 39        battery usage. MainActivity shows a one-time dialog that opens
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2222653Z 40        the system "ignore battery optimizations" screen so scheduled
2026-05-03T23:13:04.2223411Z 41        reminders are not deferred indefinitely.
